  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember they sent me once to-- they had a camp of-- for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] people who had been quite ill, which sometimes they let even young people like me go to.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I spent I think five days once in such a facility, which was helpful.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As far as outings were concerned, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at the beginning, there were very few outings.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think the first year we were not allowed to go out at all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After about a year, they let you go out maybe every three, four months, for five, six hours.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had to apply and they gave you permission and then you could-- then you could go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Eventually they let you go out more often, and even for the whole day, towards the end.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was really pretty stupid, because I don't know-- again, it was one of those unnecessary things, because you really couldn't run away from Mauritius.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no place for you to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So why they didn't let you go out, I never understand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was again one of those things that the commanders certainly should have made easier for all of us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] During-- in 1943, I believe it was, suddenly they stopped all outings without any explanation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't know why, until later on we found out that there were some Japanese submarines near the island and they had sunk several vessels.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the food, which had to be imported to Mauritius, was getting scarce.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
